name: Goblin Researcher
oracle_text: When Goblin Researcher enters the battlefield, exile the top card of your library. During any turn you attacked with Goblin Researcher, you may play that card.
flavor_text: Slonk was struck by lightning twenty-seven times before he got the idea. Another forty-three hits and he'd perfected it.

name: Daring Piracy
oracle_text: At the beginning of your combat on your turn, create a 1/1 red Pirate creature token with menace and haste. Exile it at the beginning of the next end step.
flavor_text: Sky pirates often leap randomly into the fray and assume there will be something to land on.

name: Coalborn Entity
oracle_text: {2}{R}: Coalborn Entity deals 1 damage to target creature token, player, or planeswalker.
flavor_text: The blacksmith forgot to feed the forge, so the forge fed itself.

name: Brazen Cannonade
oracle_text:
Whenever an attacking creature you control dies, Brazen Cannonade deals 2 damage to each opponent.
Raid — At the beginning of your precombat main phase, if you attacked with a creature this turn, exile the top card of your library. Until end of combat on your next turn, you may play that card.

name: Auntie Blyte, Bad Influence
oracle_text:
Flying
Whenever a source you control deals damage to you, put that many +1/+1 counters on Auntie Blyte, Bad Influence.
{1}{R}, {T}, Remove X +1/+1 counters from Auntie Blyte: It deals X damage to any target.

name: Suspicious Shambler
oracle_text: {4}{B}{B}, Exile Suspicious Shambler from your graveyard: Create two 2/2 black Zombie creature tokens. Activate only as a sorcery.
flavor_text: It was the perfect disguise—at least until its stomach started moaning.

name: Skullslither Worm
oracle_text: When Skullslither Worm enters the battelfield, each opponent discards a card. For each opponent who can't, put two +1/+1 counters on Skullslither Worm.
flavor_text: As larvae, they burrow into a host's brain to feed upon it, growing until they're large enough to burst free and seek out larger prey.

name: Ossuary Rats
oracle_text: When Ossuary Rats enters the battlefield, it deals X damage to target creature or planeswalker an opponent controls, where X is the number of creature cards in your graveyard.
flavor_text: You know you've ventured too deep when the rats stop running and hold their ground.

name: Deadly Plot
oracle_text:
Choose one —
• Destroy target creature or planeswalker.
• Return target Zombie creature card from your graveyard to the battlefield tapped.
flavor_text:
"Open grave available, only one previous tenant."
—Sign on cemetery gate

name: Launch Mishap
oracle_text: Counter target creature or planeswalker spell. Create a 1/1 colorless Thopter artifact creature token with flying.

oracle_text:

{3}{G/U}: Look at the top card of yhour library. If it's a Kraken, Leviathan, Octopus, or Serpent creature card, you may put it onto the battlefield. If you don't put the card onto the battlefield, you may put it on the bottom of your library.

name: Biblioplex Kraken
oracle_text:
When Biblioplex Kraken enters the battlefield, scry 3. (Look at the top three cards of your library, then put any number of them on the bottom of your library and the rest on top in any order.)
Whenever Biblioplex Kraken attacks, you may return another creature you control to its owner's hand. If you do, Biblioplex Kraken can't be blocked this turn.

oracle_text:
